001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.models;
002
003import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.Message;
004
005import java.util.HashSet;
006import java.util.Set;
007
008public abstract class NotificationMessage extends Message {
009
010    public boolean isEmpty() {
011        return size()==0;
012    }
013
014    public abstract int size();
015
016    /**
017     * @return notification IDs which, if present in
018     * {@link com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.currentStatus.MalfunctionStatusResponse}
019     * should hide the associated malfunction response
020     */
021    public Set<Integer> notificationIds() {
022        return new HashSet<>();
023    }
024
025}
